            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Crush your<strong> garlic cloves</strong> open by squashing them with the side of a knife and remove the skins</p><p>Crush your <strong>cardamom pods </strong>open by squashing them with the side of a knife</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
