            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Use this time to clear up, set the table, have a cup of tea or simply chill!</p><p>Once the curry is almost done, discard the <strong>cardamom pods</strong></p><p>Add your<strong> naan[s]</strong> to a baking tray and put the tray in the oven for 3-4 min or until warmed through</p><p>Tip: Cooking for 3 or more? Use 2 trays!</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
