    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the<strong> one-pot chicken rogan josh</strong> with the <strong>warmed naan</strong> to the side</p><p>Dollop your <strong>natural yoghurt </strong>over the top of the chicken rogan josh</p><p>Dig in!</p>",
